I know it’s been a while since I shared hair care tips, but I’m back with a simple yet powerful drink that works wonders for both your hair and skin!
Just blend a few gooseberries with ginger, mint, and a pinch of salt. Strain the juice, pour it into an ice cube tray, and freeze. Pop one daily for a natural boost.
Gooseberries are rich in Vitamin C and antioxidants, which help strengthen hair roots, prevent premature greying, and promote glowing skin.
